Text: Thanx navigator68. This map works fine for Windows Pocket PC with Tomtom navigator 7.910 SUPER
How do I get his working on my TomTom Start? It doesn't have a SD Card but it has 1GB of inbuilt memory.

It works for my tom tom one V3 and Start! First you format the Tomtom. Then you install a new patched version of Navcore. Then copy the new 1 gb map on the tom tom and use a program called Easydctmaker to make the map work with the device.
